{"type":"message","id":"0b36bd5c","parentId":"bc72bbeb","timestamp":"2026-03-29T17:01:11.706Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Coordinating task management**\n\nI need to coordinate tasks between Backlog and Next, ensuring there’s a clear owner for each. Currently, only Next has an owner, Ares, while the Backlog doesn't. It might help to clarify ownership across all tasks. I need to actively communicate with Ares about this. I’m considering whether to send a message regarding the decisions and next steps, including executing a send to Smart Project to confirm or address any issues.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0566585cbba6d7720169c95ad154bc8191ace5e5ac5087ea5e\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpyVrYt0mkfF45wR74C060Xu4xdKSkZD6lCmdgu9r-rs_uoiXP_lgm6snMyUPerdy4sCi7PbPyDtv7jeSay34KwwkKxtiirIdyRJt2SeJSuAirNYm6pS1BuhTiBfuQmgzDGk_9BMuMcspC4suyyDmRsfIRvU8FdZ7Ncfnaqqq57yPgwDmNbkjjRmjunqOHqK75UjFHwyX78bey5CF0P7vLVfz3Of7dX3TD-jI-Bg474KF3cj8_2Y0XGv8m0VXQ0_WVlueISxwegBQEpr0KHgIUvzQj14vIrqmXJJbJpU6OVmF1ZuRkHu-AIthQTbBYmORILAPsPm9SvFt58Y2b6QLx1lvICXyKULXZYYOYqIDpfhPRn-DIqqu1Gy5oZ1PJzGus6VtWXNqXAECoiPOlbESxGpR7R15OHi5RXefecvPyIY1xuaTZ5AmgaMMwqaxua3RKylUqpZmkWi9xkKSwzEz5O5duz4tktCF1xJygw8ioKiBFh7DTBdfwcGc-bjCVKVgL2r7GYzR3NmIK3mCS74cSUAi7MBBOzo2iSvKf1DNpT4P1T4g9Wk47OZPwVGMw6a_E8ooX50zHRxIG_DQqlzIFi9rrl4WKADQkmagq84M7RwcvN9QIuElsifxYz3SLuNpbj-AWACDwu7AzzY7DIFmbQcfoaKSPAFgeRhOlXPT3t8pgPEfZsJyxjwj2fUCwJ2_0S1op7Tav7w2gNCaUDr80ExF0mEw1sT1lV5bweQiX_2PxNm7OLWyJ60YOcMcu-Xu2MXE8GHIQ0oG2qgl2ujY09xr6U4gXFnJ-8C1Ezkb8qAXEBaINxVgQ9MnsRGfAxHQ0cz4WM49Y96B24wU1cs5L-8Q1EtYaCxbOWPS3VEEngfu_qbUCEDfmP4_-FVd2Mi3Rh4j3QZoH-G_9O0rWA3D4CUOG95N0H0WKAwlb_jbDc3BCCF_LkNSjJAkVb8hgdzrf1huk78K7s64sAOLYbhsMy1zbG_jK00f3MYsYVRMe0Ap8nNr-a8tosR59bukYtnDO_DG6qWs0X24bGdTomfeRpXXfkYjPFnSH0agTgrcKFaRc5b4YuB5EwpLd1ewNhLjsnByrIvqp4SlC_cUR5Jv6piwTKCa2-EFg13HZEAVnWyA00Bo4Z-IlUH2bTMOuE5JhBRNuvM4Z6boYSOcjueDdGSqposHo06l68cQUP62HPJTZHoenSo-EIPIa6Kb7y5_SEJw-tIltFU